Caelus Agent Notices
====================

Caelus Agent is a local-first agent command center powered by
Hermes Agent. Hermes Agent is a material runtime dependency; it supplies the
agent loop, model/provider configuration, tools, memory, integrations, and
permissions. Caelus Agent does not bundle Hermes Agent or represent it as
its own runtime.

